snippet.title: Genfanad - Alpha Trailer
snippet.description:
Genfanad is a new game inspired by games from our childhood. Explore a brand new world where you can still spend hours clicking trees or mining fish. Or whatever it is people do in games these days.

Follow our Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/rosetintedgames/genfanad (Coming in early 2022!)

Join our discord: https://discord.gg/uN3Vvsv

Visit our website: https://genfanad.com/
